inline_comments.message:
You'll need to add quite a few more env variables (we no longer have hardcoded. The most important ones are:
-      - MYSQL_USER=${MYSQL_USER}
      - MYSQL_PASSWORD=${MYSQL_PASSWORD}
      - MYSQL_DATABASE=${MYSQL_DATABASE}
      - ODL_ADMIN_USERNAME=${ODL_USER}
      - ODL_ADMIN_PASSWORD=${ODL_PASSWORD}
      - ODL_USER=${ODL_USER}
      - ODL_PASSWORD=${ODL_PASSWORD}

Note that the values above are env variables.  That's probably preferable to make it easier to stay consistent.
